address: Phường 14, Quận Gò Vấp, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh
thought:
**My Analysis of the Administrative Changes for "Phường 14, Quận Gò Vấp, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh"**

Okay, here's what I've determined after thoroughly examining the provided resolutions. The user is asking about the new administrative unit for "Phường 14, Quận Gò Vấp, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh." My first step was to verify the province, ensuring "Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh" remained unchanged, which it does based on resolution "60-NQ/TW".

Next, I zeroed in on the "Other resolutions" section, specifically resolution "1685/NQ-UBTVQH15," the one concerning administrative rearrangements within Ho Chi Minh City. I meticulously scanned the lines, looking for any mention of "Phường 14" within "Quận Gò Vấp".

The crucial finding: Line 52 of that resolution states, "Sắp xếp toàn bộ diện tích tự nhiên, quy mô dân số của Phường 12 và Phường 14 (quận Gò Vấp) thành phường mới có tên gọi là **phường An Hội Tây**."  This directly addresses the user's query: Phường 14 is consolidated into a new ward called "An Hội Tây". I double-checked for any other references to Phường 14 within the document to rule out competing reorganizations, but there were none.

To be extra certain, I then verified "phường An Hội Tây" in the "New wards" list, confirming its existence and code:  `{"ward_code":"26882","ward_name":"Phường An Hội Tây","province_name":"Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh"}`.

Considering this direct, explicit mapping outlined in the resolution, I have high confidence in this determination. Therefore, the new administrative unit for "Phường 14, Quận Gò Vấp, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh" is "phường An Hội Tây".
